title: Tragically Hip. Kingston, Ontario, 08-20-2016 DVD5
description:
Ready to be burned to a single layer DVD this is The Hip at their finest!
Recorded using FRAPS in real time the source files were 158 gigs so be prepared for great quality!
One apology to give is every 4 minutes of this show was a 4 gig single file and in the process of converting it for DVD use there will be a slight pause at those times.
